These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-1::.
7 different pets are kept: hamster, horse, dog, chinchilla, turtle, ferret, goldfish
The people's birthday is in 7 different months: february, september, july, december, october, november, may
 1. the owner of the hamster is between the owner of the chinchilla and the owner of the goldfish##2
 2. the owner of the horse is in the middle##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
 4. the owner of the turtle is between the person who's birthday is in july and the person who's birthday is in october##2
 5. the person who's birthday is in september is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in september is on the right of the owner of the chinchilla##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in february is between the person who's birthday is in december and the person who's birthday is in july##2
 8. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left of the owner of the goldfish##1
 9. the owner of the turtle is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1
10. the owner of the turtle is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1
11. the owner of the ferret is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |    3    |     4     |     5      |     6      |    7    |
| Pet   | chinchilla | hamster | goldfish | horse    | dog | turtle   | ferret    |
| Birthday         | november  | september   | december | february | july   | may | october |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-2::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: western, documentary, mystery, crime, scientific, comedy, family
House: cape-cod, cottage, art-deco, modern, craftsman, ranch-style, palace
1. the ranch-style house is on the far left##1
2. the person watching mystery movies is between the person watching comedy movies and the ranch-style house##2
3. the cottage house is on the right of the cape-cod house##1
4. the person watching family movies is on the right of the art-deco house##1
5. the person watching documentary movies is in the middle##1
6. the craftsman house is on the left of the cape-cod house##1
7. the palace house is on the left of the person watching documentary movies##1
8. the person watching scientific movies is on the left of the modern house##1
9. the person watching crime movies is on the right of the cape-cod house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |      3      |      4      |    5    |     6      |    7    |
| Movie-Genre          | scientific | mystery | comedy | documentary | family | western      | crime  |
| House   | ranch-style | modern  | palace     | art-deco     | craftsman  | cape-cod | cottage |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-3::.
The people have 7 different hobbies: chess, photography, singing, camping, video-games, drawing, board-games
There are 7 different favourite colors: purple, grey, white, amber, light-blue, ebony, blue
 1. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is chess##1
 2. the person who likes white is on the left of the person who likes amber##1
 3. the person who likes light-blue is the person who's hobby is board-games##1
 4. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
 5. the person who likes purple is on the left of the person who likes blue##1
 6. the person who's hobby is camping is the person who likes amber##1
 7. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left of the person who likes white##1
 8. the person who likes purple is between the person who likes blue and the person who's hobby is camping##2
 9. the person who's hobby is chess is on the right of the person who likes ebony##1
10. the person who's hobby is photography is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |    3     |    4    |   5    |   6    |     7     |
| Hobby   | board-games | video-games | chess | photography   | camping | singing | drawing |
| Color           | light-blue | ebony     | grey     | white | amber   | purple   | blue    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-4::.
7 different brands of cigars are smoked: swisher, bongani, tiparillo, old-henry, havana, bolivar, alhambra
The people have 7 different hobbies: woodworking, traveling, hiking, singing, gardening, writing, photography
 1. the alhambra-smoker is on the left of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
 2. the havana-smoker is on the right of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
 3. the person who's hobby is writing is on the right of the person who's hobby is singing##1
 4. the havana-smoker is on the right of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
 5. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the right of the swisher-smoker##1
 6. the person who's hobby is singing is between the tiparillo-smoker and the person who's hobby is writing##2
 7. the swisher-smoker is in the middle##1
 8. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left of the old-henry-smoker##1
 9. the bongani-smoker is the person who's hobby is traveling##1
10. the person who's hobby is woodworking is the alhambra-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3     |   4    |     5      |     6     |    7     |
| Cigar      | tiparillo    | havana  | old-henry  | swisher  | alhambra      | bolivar       | bongani |
| Hobby   | gardening | singing | writing | photography | woodworking | hiking | traveling  |

