.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-5::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  firefighter, electrician, social-worker, bartender, writer, librarian, dressmaker
7 different pets are kept: horse, mouse, guinea-pig, dog, turtle, bird, fish
1. the owner of the dog is on the right of the owner of the turtle##1
2. the owner of the turtle is the electrician##1
3. the owner of the horse is between the dressmaker and the firefighter##2
4. the librarian is on the right of the owner of the turtle##1
5. the owner of the horse is in the middle##1
6. the owner of the bird is on the left of the firefighter##1
7. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the owner of the turtle##1
8. the owner of the mouse is the bartender##1
9. the writer is the owner of the bird##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2   |     3     |  4   |     5     |     6      |  7   |
| Job   | bartender      | writer | firefighter | social-worker | dressmaker      | electrician      | librarian |
| Pet     | mouse | bird | fish       | horse | guinea-pig | turtle | dog |

