.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-6::.
City: rome, new-york, miami, liverpool, hannover, paris, venice
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: zombie, adventure, fantasy, time-travel, sports, mystery, spy
1. the person traveling to miami is on the left of the person traveling to venice##1
2. the person watching fantasy movies is the person traveling to hannover##1
3. the person watching zombie movies is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1
4. the person traveling to new-york is on the left of the person watching zombie movies##1
5. the person traveling to paris is on the right of the person watching spy movies##1
6. the person watching spy movies is between the person watching sports movies and the person traveling to rome##2
7. the person watching sports movies is on the left of the person watching adventure movies##1
8. the person traveling to paris is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |      2      |        3        |      4       |     5     |     6     |   7    |
| City     | hannover | rome | liverpool | paris | new-york | miami     | venice |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy   | time-travel    | spy    | sports      | adventure  | zombie | mystery |

