.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-7::.
7 different brands of cigars are smoked: alhambra, aristoff, pall-mall, dannemann, davidoff, fonseca, prince
There 7 different types of food: kale, cabbage, pear, kiwi, cucumber, blueberry, apple
 1. the person eating blueberry is the davidoff-smoker##1
 2. the aristoff-smoker is on the left of the person eating apple##1
 3. the person eating cabbage is in the middle##1
 4. the pall-mall-smoker is between the person eating cucumber and the person eating apple##2
 5. the person eating kale is on the left of the dannemann-smoker##1
 6. the alhambra-smoker is on the left of the person eating kale##1
 7. the person eating kiwi is the alhambra-smoker##1
 8. the fonseca-smoker is the person eating cucumber##1
 9. the person eating pear is between the person eating cucumber and the davidoff-smoker##2
10. the pall-mall-smoker is on the left of the fonseca-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |       3       |    4    |    5     |    6    |    7     |
| Cigar   | alhambra | aristoff    | dannemann | pall-mall   | fonseca | prince    | davidoff |
| Food      | kiwi | kale | apple    | cabbage | cucumber    | pear | blueberry  |

