.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-8::.
7 different pets are kept: snake, rat, rabbit, goldfish, pony, horse, dog
There are 7 different nationalities: american, thai, dutch, canadian, malaysian, russian, polish
 1. the malaysian is on the left of the canadian##1
 2. the american is on the left of the dutch##1
 3. the russian is on the far left##1
 4. the owner of the rat is on the left of the owner of the dog##1
 5. the malaysian is on the left of the owner of the rat##1
 6. the owner of the horse is between the owner of the goldfish and the owner of the dog##2
 7. the thai is on the right of the russian##1
 8. the american is on the right of the owner of the dog##1
 9. the owner of the rat is on the right of the owner of the snake##1
10. the owner of the rat is between the owner of the dog and the owner of the snake##2
11. the malaysian is on the right of the owner of the pony##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1        |     2      |      3       |     4     |         5          |     6      |     7     |
| Pet   | rabbit  | pony   | snake         | rat     | dog              | horse    | goldfish     |
| Nationality        | russian | thai | malaysian | canadian | polish | american | dutch |

