2. the tower house is on the left of the person who likes ivory##1
3. the person who likes ebony is between the farmhouse house and the townhouse house##2
4. the person who likes aquamarine is on the left of the person who likes apricot##1
5. the cape-cod house is in the middle##1
6. the person who likes ebony is on the left of the person who likes grey##1
7. the victorian house is on the left of the townhouse house##1
8. the person who likes ebony is on the right of the person who likes blue##1
