.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-10::.
There 7 different types of food: garlic, pear, cherry, onion, tomato, pepper, lime
There are 7 different nationalities: italian, french, american, japanese, indian, mexican, australian
1. the mexican is the person eating cherry##1
2. the person eating garlic is on the right of the person eating pear##1
3. the american is on the right of the person eating pear##1
4. the mexican is between the japanese and the french##2
5. the australian is on the left of the american##1
6. the japanese is on the far right##1
7. the person eating lime is on the right of the person eating garlic##1
8. the person eating onion is between the person eating tomato and the mexican##2
9. the indian is on the right of the italian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2     |      3      |      4       |    5    |      6      |    7    |
| Food   | pear  | garlic       | lime         | tomato         | onion   | cherry        | pepper |
| Nationality      | australian | american | italian | indian | french | mexican | japanese  |

