City: london, liverpool, boston, hannover, rome, miami, paris
1. the person traveling to paris is on the far right##1
2. the prince-smoker is on the right of the person traveling to liverpool##1
3. the swisher-smoker is in the middle##1
4. the aristoff-smoker is on the right of the person traveling to london##1
5. the person traveling to london is on the right of the person traveling to boston##1
6. the pall-mall-smoker is between the person traveling to rome and the ritmeester-smoker##2
7. the prince-smoker is between the dannemann-smoker and the siglo-smoker##2
8. the siglo-smoker is on the left of the person traveling to hannover##1
9. the ritmeester-smoker is on the left of the aristoff-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |       2       |     3      |       4       |    5    |     6      |       7       |
| Cigar   | siglo | prince       | dannemann    | swisher | pall-mall | ritmeester     | aristoff       |
