.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-12::.
7 different pets are kept: chinchilla, goat, dog, lizard, guinea-pig, pony, fish
7 different games are played: canasta, bridge, snooker, go, poker, chess, domino
 1. the owner of the chinchilla is the person playing domino##1
 2. the owner of the fish is on the left of the person playing poker##1
 3. the owner of the chinchilla is between the owner of the lizard and the person playing canasta##2
 4. the owner of the pony is between the owner of the fish and the owner of the guinea-pig##2
 5. the person playing chess is on the right of the person playing snooker##1
 6. the person playing snooker is on the right of the person playing canasta##1
 7. the owner of the dog is on the far right##1
 8. the owner of the dog is the person playing poker##1
 9. the person playing go is on the far left##1
10. the person playing go is the owner of the lizard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3   |   4   |    5    |   6    |   7    |
| Pet   | lizard | chinchilla | goat  | guinea-pig   | pony | fish | dog |
| Game   | go     | domino       | canasta | snooker | chess  | bridge   | poker   |

