.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-13::.
7 different games are played: backgammon, scrabble, bridge, canasta, whist, billiard, domino
The people have 7 different jobs:  electrician, designer, journalist, teacher, writer, fisherman, bartender
 1. the electrician is on the left of the writer##1
 2. the designer is on the left of the person playing canasta##1
 3. the person playing billiard is between the electrician and the person playing whist##2
 4. the person playing domino is between the person playing canasta and the person playing whist##2
 5. the journalist is on the left of the electrician##1
 6. the person playing whist is on the right of the writer##1
 7. the journalist is on the right of the person playing backgammon##1
 8. the bartender is on the right of the person playing billiard##1
 9. the teacher is on the left of the person playing bridge##1
10. the person playing bridge is on the left of the person playing scrabble##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2   |      3      |   4    |    5    |   6   |    7     |
| Game      | backgammon   | bridge | scrabble | billiard | whist | domino   | canasta |
| Job   | teacher | journalist | electrician     | writer | bartender  | designer | fisherman     |

