The people's birthday is in 7 different months: february, november, may, august, january, april, july
 1. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1
 2. the person who's hobby is writing is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1
 3. the person who's hobby is video-games is the person who's birthday is in february##1
 4. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the far left##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in may is the person who's hobby is singing##1
 7. the person who's hobby is woodworking is the person who's birthday is in april##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in november is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1
 9. the person who's hobby is gardening is between the person who's hobby is drawing and the person who's birthday is in may##2
10. the person who's hobby is woodworking is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2     |   3   |   4    |   5    |    6    |   7    |
