.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-15::.
City: berlin, liverpool, miami, hamburg, boston, london, paris
7 different games are played: go, canasta, bridge, mah-jongg, backgammon, billiard, monopoly
 1. the person traveling to paris is on the right of the person playing monopoly##1
 2. the person traveling to liverpool is in the middle##1
 3. the person playing backgammon is on the right of the person traveling to london##1
 4. the person traveling to miami is between the person traveling to paris and the person playing go##2
 5. the person playing mah-jongg is the person traveling to miami##1
 6. the person traveling to berlin is on the left of the person traveling to london##1
 7. the person playing monopoly is the person traveling to liverpool##1
 8. the person playing bridge is the person playing bridge##1
 9. the person traveling to liverpool is on the left of the person playing canasta##1
10. the person playing bridge is on the left of the person traveling to boston##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2    |     3     |       4       |      5      |    6     |    7     |
| City   | berlin       | london | boston      | liverpool | paris       | miami | hamburg |
| Game       | billiard | bridge    | backgammon | monopoly    | canasta | mah-jongg   | go |

